1. We convert the three txt file datasets into their respective json files by using the 
      Notebandi_tweets.txt ----> tweets_txt_to_json.py ----> Notebandi_tweets.json
      Notebandi_tweets_with_language.txt ----> tweets_with_lang_to_json.py ----> Notebandi_tweets_with_language.json
      Notebandi_tweets_stance.txt ----> tweets_stance_to_json.py ----> Notebandi_tweets_stance.json

